Service for AMs of Saturday, March 13:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL &LR;  (``i'' code)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATO &LR;
</P>
<P>
   NATO (Independence, Mo.) _ In a ceremony at the Truman Library
attended by the foreign ministers of the alliance, Poland, Hungary
and the Czech Republic formally join NATO. By Jane Perlez.
</P>
<P>
   With a chronology graphic.
