   With
</P>
<P>
   NATO-ASSESS (Independence) _ A news analysis on the history and
significance of the three former Warsaw Pact nations joining NATO.
By R.W. Apple Jr.
</P>
<P>
   And
</P>
<P>
   NATO-POLAND-SCENE (Warsaw) _ The scene in Warsaw on the big day.
By Steven Erlanger.
