MIRAMAX-OSCARS (Los Angeles) _ Oscar voters' tastes have shifted to
independent film companies and Miramax is at the forefront. (Runs
with sidebar slugged MIRAMAX-FILMS). By Reed Johnson. 
 
 
KAZAN-CONTROVERSY (Los Angeles) _ The academy's decision to honor
Elia Kazan, who turned government informant during the red scare,
has reopend an old wound. Bob Strauss. 

<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-03-12-99 2036EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
